name: automized_bindings_generation
description: This project parses given javascript dir and generates ns bindings if necessary
readme:
# Extend_Class_Generator
This project is an automatized build to generate all necessary extend bindings, form a nativescript project.

## preparation
- project expects you to put jars in JARS folder, so they can be parsed and all interfaces names extracted from them
- project expects you to provide js user code in JSCODE
- run 'npm install' to be able to run grunt

## how to start
- just run grunt
- output will go in DIST folder, which will be in the project root dir if no other outDir is specified
